        <p>Given the number of responders, s, in the first 25 patients for the 1<sup>st</sup> stage, we calculate predictive probability of 21-s or more responders in the remaining 25 patients, i.e.,</p>
        <disp-formula id="e19">
          <mml:math id="m24" display="block" overflow="scroll">
            <mml:mrow>
              <mml:mstyle displaystyle="true">
